The,American,Express,Payment,Software,Developer,Kit,SDK,gives,users,the,tools,needed,to,build,applications,on,the,American,Express,network,The,SDK,allows,developers,to,manage,the,communication,and,compliance,elements,for,secure,integration,and,transaction,processing,The,SDK,interfaces,with,American,Express,s,Payments,API,platform,Internet,Direct,allowing,merchants,to,avoid,processing,fees,and,minimize,potential,points,of,failure